organizations.name: corrections & amplifications fourth corner credit union

text:
Fourth Corner Credit Union plans to serve individuals and companies supporting legalized marijuana, including those partnering with vendors, such as accountants and landlords. A Business & Finance article Tuesday about the Colorado credit union incorrectly said the company also would serve lawyers linked to marijuana businesses.
